}}'''2020年尼日利亞抗議'''（End Special Anti-Robbery Squad，簡稱End SARS或#EndSARS）是2020年10月發生在[[奈及利亞|尼日利亚]]的一場該國人民反对[[警察暴力|警察暴力]]的社会运动。示威群眾呼吁當局解散[[特别反抢劫行动队|特别反抢劫行动队]]（SARS）<ref>{{Cite web|title=外媒：尼日利亚军方向反警暴抗议者开枪，已致6人死亡|url=https://m.jiemian.com/article/5144668.html|accessdate=|author=界面新聞|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2020-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026062432/https://m.jiemian.com/article/5144668.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，这是尼日利亚一支备受争议的警察特种部队，特别反抢劫行动队被指控长期滋擾、恐嚇和虐待尼日利亞人民。<ref name="END SARS">{{Cite news|author=Kingsley|first=Omonobi|title=Anti-SARS campaign: IG orders investigation of anti-robbery squad|url=https://www.vanguardngr.com/2017/12/anti-sars-campaign-ig-orders-investigation-anti-robbery-squad/|accessdate=31 January 2018|work=Vanguard Newspaper|location=Nigeria|date=4 December 2017|archive-date=2018-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180131092827/https://www.vanguardngr.com/2017/12/anti-sars-campaign-ig-orders-investigation-anti-robbery-squad/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=外媒：尼日利亚军方向反警暴抗议者开枪，已致6人死亡|url=https://finance.sina.cn/tech/2020-10-21/detail-iiznctkc6767204.d.html?fromtech=1|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=[[界面新聞|界面新聞]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024164338/https://finance.sina.cn/tech/2020-10-21/detail-iiznctkc6767204.d.html?fromtech=1|archive-date=2020-10-24|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=尼日利亚的“SARS病毒”：反警察暴力抗议背后难解的困境|url=https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_9730253|access-date=2021-06-12|date=2020-10-27|work=[[澎湃新闻|澎湃新闻]]|language=zh|archive-date=2021-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210612151608/https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_9730253|dead-url=no}}</ref>

早在2017年，尼日利亞人民就在[[Twitter|Twitter]]上發佈帶有#ENDSARS的[[主題標籤|主题标签]]的推文，要求尼日利亚政府解決特别反抢劫行动队引發的暴力問題。<ref name="Salaudeen2017">{{Cite news|author=Salaudeen|first=Aisha|title=Nigerians want police's SARS force scrapped|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2017/12/nigerians-demand-police-sars-unit-171215153831230.html|accessdate=2 January 2018|publisher=Aljazeera|date=15 December 2017|archive-date=2018-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180102012506/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2017/12/nigerians-demand-police-sars-unit-171215153831230.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=End SARS as a Mob Project|url=https://www.thisdaylive.com/index.php/2017/12/17/end-sars-as-a-mob-project/|accessdate=2 January 2018|publisher=Thisday Newspapers Limited|location=Nigeria|date=17 December 2017|archive-date=2018-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180103011703/https://www.thisdaylive.com/index.php/2017/12/17/end-sars-as-a-mob-project/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|author=Ogundipe|first=Samuel|title=#EndSARS: Police mum as Nigerians recount atrocities of Special Anti-Robbery Squad|url=https://www.premiumtimesng.com/news/headlines/251271-endsars-police-mum-nigerians-recount-atrocities-special-anti-robbery-squad.html|accessdate=2 January 2018|publisher=Premium Times|location=Nigeria|date=December 3, 2017|archive-date=2018-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180103011700/https://www.premiumtimesng.com/news/headlines/251271-endsars-police-mum-nigerians-recount-atrocities-special-anti-robbery-squad.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2020年10月，反對特别反抢劫行动队的運動捲土重來，尼日利亚的主要城市均发生[[示威|大规模示威活动]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=How a youth-led digital movement is driving Nigeria's largest protests in a decade|url=https://qz.com/africa/1916319/how-nigerians-use-social-media-to-organize-endsars-protests/|accessdate=2020-10-13|author=Kazeem|first=Yomi|work=Quartz Africa|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201013223049/https://qz.com/africa/1916319/how-nigerians-use-social-media-to-organize-endsars-protests/|dead-url=no}}</ref>同時尼日利亚人還在推特上分享有關特别反抢劫行动队成员在尼日利亚从事绑架、谋杀、盗窃、强奸、施加酷刑、非法逮捕、侮辱、[[非法拘禁|非法拘留]]，法外处决和勒索的事跡和视频<ref>http://www.endsars.com {{Wayback|url=http://www.endsars.com/ |date=20201210102612 }} Endsars</ref>。2020年10月11日，尼日利亞當局宣佈解散特别反抢劫行动队。<ref>{{Cite web|title=#EndSARS: Nigeria says Special Anti-Robbery Squad dissolved|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/10/11/endsars-nigeria-dissolves-special-anti-robbery-squad|accessdate=11 October 2020|author=|date=11 October 2020|first=|work=Al Jazeera|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201011213111/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/10/11/endsars-nigeria-dissolves-special-anti-robbery-squad|archivedate=2020-10-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>但是有许多人指出，其實尼日利亞當局近年来也做出過类似的承诺，但並未兌現。而此次尼日利亞當局只是將特别反抢劫行动队的負責人調整至其他部門，而不是完全将其撤职。<ref name="Ademoroti">{{Cite web|title=What It Means When the Police Say They are Dissolving SARS|url=https://www.bellanaija.com/2020/10/what-it-means-when-the-police-say-they-are-dissolving-sars/|accessdate=11 October 2020|author=Ademoroti|date=11 October 2020|first=Niyi|work=BellaNaija|archive-date=2020-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201011170410/https://www.bellanaija.com/2020/10/what-it-means-when-the-police-say-they-are-dissolving-sars/|dead-url=no}}</ref>因此抗议活动繼續進行，尼日利亚政府選擇暴力镇压示威者，有示威者在衝突中喪生。<ref name="auto">{{Cite web|title=Another #EndSARS protester shot dead {{!}} Premium Times Nigeria|url=https://www.premiumtimesng.com/news/headlines/420205-just-in-another-endsars-protester-shot-dead.html|accessdate=2020-10-12|date=2020-10-12|language=en-GB|archive-date=2020-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201013002519/https://www.premiumtimesng.com/news/headlines/420205-just-in-another-endsars-protester-shot-dead.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年10月19日，示威者袭击了两所位于[[贝宁城|贝宁城]]的监狱，导致约2000名囚犯越狱。由於示威持續，10月20日起，[[拉各斯州|拉各斯州]]实施24小时戒严<ref>{{Cite web|title=尼日利亚局势升级：拉各斯全面戒严，监狱遭袭两千囚犯逃出|url=https://www.sohu.com/a/426311179_260616|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=[[澎湃新聞|澎湃新聞]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023052351/https://www.sohu.com/a/426311179_260616|archive-date=2020-10-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

